yan-hymel-heroique-french-opera-arias/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> Bryan Hymel: Hroque &#8211; French Opera Arias</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2015/09/felice-romani-e-i-suoi-melodrammi-giulietta-e-romeo-di-nicola-vaccaj/" rel="next">Felice Romani e i suoi melodrammi: &#8220;Giulietta e Romeo&#8221; di Nicola Vaccaj <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"><h2 class="comments-title"> 1 comment</h2><ol class="commentlist"><li class="pingback even thread-even depth-1" id="comment-119221"><p>Pingback: <a href=\'https://operabellasite.wordpress.com/2016/05/25/le-nozze-di-figaro-al-teatro-fraschini-di-pavia/\' rel=\'external nofollow\' class=\'url\'>LE NOZZE DI FIGARO AL TEATRO FRASCHINI DI PAVIA &#8211; Opera Bella</a></p></li></ol><div id="respond" class="comment-respond"><h3 id="reply-title" class="comment-reply-title">Lascia un commento <small><a rel="nofollow" id="cancel-comment-reply-link" href="/2015/09/operalombardia-como-teatro-sociale-le-nozze-di-figaro/#respond" style="display:none;">Annulla risposta</a></small></h3><form action="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-comments-post.php" method="post" id="commentform" class="comment-form"><p class="comment-notes"><span id="email-notes">Il tuo indirizzo email non sar pubblicato.</span> I campi obbligatori sono contrassegnati <span class="required">*</span></p><p class="comment-form-comment"><label for="comment">Commento</label><textarea id="comment" name="comment" cols="45" rows="8" maxlength="65525" aria-required="true" required="required"></textarea></p><p class="comment-form-author"><label for="author">Nome <span class="required">*</span></label> <input id="author" name="author" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="245" aria-r